Then, As Now

My wish 
is for a love 
long and everlasting
an embrace
not of beauty or youth
but of a bond 
that will not only weather 
all storms
but when one day 
as weathered as the storm
still holds fast
still holds true
and stirs 
the same depth of love 
then 
as now
between me and you

Morning musings by
Tammi Keech 
2020
